請以本題所描述的情境，討論資訊不對稱下所可能產生的道德危機與
逆選擇問題。（6分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fc6a0a3b10e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "財政學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00316', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-f6a9be68', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'essay', '某筆土地每年可帶來 120,000 元租金收入，直到永久。請回答下列有關
